node.text:
Have u tried @ajifuku_sg ? Tempura and tendon specialist Ajifuku has affordable tendons waiting for you. 
1️⃣ Ebi Tamago Don
2️⃣ Egg Chicken Katsu Don
3️⃣ Unagi Tendon
4️⃣ Curry Udon with Chicken Katsu 
5️⃣ Kimuchi Udon with Chiken Katsu
6️⃣ Takoyaki balls 
If you crave for Japanese-style rice bowls, but have no plans to head to Japan anytime soon, you can check out Ajifuku. It specialises in hearty and affordable don and katsu. Tender, flavourful meats, consistent fluffy eggs, and its hearty portion ~ 
Takeaway and Delivery available

Address: 50 Jurong Gateway Rd. #03-27 Jem, Singapore 608549 🇸🇬 (Donki food court)
10am to 10pm
